      "text": "**Defining Core Features**\n\nI'm currently focused on defining the core features for this React application. I've begun detailing the church and leader management functionalities, specifically the necessary fields like name, contact information, and community association. This initial phase helps shape the scope and direction.\n\n\n**Expanding Feature Scope**\n\nI've significantly expanded the application's feature set. Now I'm including zone management with grouping, filtering, and stats. Meeting management, incorporating church assignment, is also underway. WhatsApp integration, both individual and bulk, via an API and dynamic variables, will be included, as well as a dashboard, excel import and a modern architecture for the application. I've also outlined the initial file structure and key data models.\n\n\n**Refining User Interface**\n\nI'm now focusing on user interface details. I've chosen Lucide-React for icons and a clean, professional blue and white color scheme. Responsive sidebar navigation is also a priority. I'm actively working on dashboards, searchable church tables with filters, meeting lists, and a messaging template editor. I will integrate Gemini API for intelligent message creation. I'm also planning the data structures.\n\n\n",
