      "type": "thinking",
      "text": "**Prioritizing Meeting Cards**\n\nI'm currently focused on ordering the meeting cards. Right now, I'm examining how `dynamicMeetings` is created within `MeetingManagement.tsx`. My goal is to sort these based on the `meetingId` (or `reunion_asignada` from Columna K), arranging them from 1 to 5. The sorting logic needs to be integrated, ensuring the cards display in the correct sequence.\n\n\n**Sorting Meeting Data**\n\nI'm now diving into sorting the `dynamicMeetings` array within `MeetingManagement.tsx`. It appears the current implementation fetches unique `meetingId` values. My focus is on integrating a numerical sort based on this `meetingId`. I'll need to handle potential string formats like \"Reunión 1\" or just \"1\". I'm planning to extract the numerical portion using regex or parsing, ensuring an ascending order.\n\n\n",
