      "type": "thinking",
      "text": "**Revising Territorial View**\n\nI'm currently focused on the \"Calendario\" view. My initial plan involved a card/grid display for church groups, categorized by zone and meeting. The core idea is to navigate to a detailed view upon clicking a card, showcasing specifics of that group. That's the primary architecture. Now I need to design the data and functionality for the detail view.\n\n\n**Refining Grouping & Details**\n\nI'm now refining the grouping logic in `MeetingManagement.tsx` to combine \"Zone\" and \"Meeting Group.\" The goal is distinct cards for unique groups, representing invitation batches. Next, I'll update the `meeting-detail` view within `App.tsx`. This includes scheduling inputs for date/venue and a \"Bulk Send\" button for WhatsApp messaging. The update will be dynamic, handling local state for any updates on meeting data.\n\n\n",
