      "text": "**Considering Data Persistence**\n\nI'm focusing on ensuring data persistence across the application. Currently, churches use `localStorage`, but I must also figure out how to handle the `meetingSchedule`, `groupTemplate`, and configurations. This must be resilient after closing the program or after any updates.\n\n\n**Expanding Data Storage**\n\nI've determined I need to expand the storage strategy. I plan to store `meetingSchedules` and `groupTemplates` indexed by group ID, and also store the `activeGroup` if the user was in a specific view. This necessitates a new storage key for \"Group Configurations.\" I'm updating `App.tsx` accordingly. I also need to make sure the \"Sede de reunion\" from column (I) is correctly persisted.\n\n\n",
